      div(class="row justify-content-between")
        div(class="col-12 col-md-7")
          h6.text-light Disclaimers
          p(class="text-justify text-light") Obey Me! Collection is a web resource created by fans. Creators of the website are not in any way affiliated with NTT Solmare Corporation. All characters, illustrations, and game content are copyrighted work exclusively belonging to NTT Solmare Corporation.
        div(class="col-6 col-md-4")
          h6(class="text-light") Links
          ul(class="footer-links text-light")
            li Download for&nbsp;
              a(class="text-light" href="https://apps.apple.com/app/obey-me-shall-we-date/id1477167654") <u>iOS</u>&nbsp;
              | and&nbsp;
              a(class="text-light" href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.nttsolmare.game.android.obeyme") <u>Android</u>&nbsp;
            li
              a.text-light(href="https://shallwedate.jp/obeyme/en/") Official Website
            li
              a(class="text-light" href="https://www.facebook.com/obeyme.solmare/") Obey Me! Official Facebook
            li
              a(class="text-light" href="https://obey-me.fandom.com/wiki/Obey_Me!_Wiki") Obey Me! Wiki
            li
              a(class="text-light" href="https://www.reddit.com/r/obeyme/") Obey Me! Subreddit
